asset.title: Silverado, Suburban, Tahoe, Avalanche, GMC Sierra 1500/2500, Yukon, Denali Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to select 1999-2007 Chevy Silverado, Suburban, Tahoe, Avalanche, GMC Sierra 1500/2500, Yukon, Denali 4.8L, 5.3L and 6.0L. 

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=77-3023KP

K&N dynamometer tests show an estimated 14.06 horsepower gain at 4897 RPM with use of this K&N air intake system. K&N tests multiple vehicles for each air intake system it makes to ensure a consistent horsepower and torque gain. 

Check http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=77-3023KP for more info and an up to date list of models this air intake fits

Search for your own vehicle's corresponding part here:
http://www.KNfilters.com
